There was nothing going on yesterday so I didn&#039;t post. To see what I capped check out the site.

Suprisingly it was another slow night. The highlight was James & Chelsia kissing. He tried to get her about 20 times and she kept on rejecting him, after a while it was hard to watch.

As it stands right now I think Alex/Amanda & Sheila/Adam will be on the block with Matt/Nat going on if one of them wins POV. It could be interesting as the house is slowing turning on Allison & Sheila.

Part 1 - 13 min

Part 4 - 24 min
Sheila goes absoutely ballistic on Adam - Then sheila bitches to Allison about Adam. She&#039;s the biggest bitch in BB history.

Part 5 - 8 min

Part 6 - 16 min
James & Chelsia get drunk in the HOH. They talk about the game & James admits that he likes her.

Part 7 - 6 min
James & Chelsia make out in the HOH room.

Part 8 - 18 min

Part 9 - 10 min
